Source: php-json-schema
Section: php
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Volker Theile <votdev@gmx.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.8)
Standards-Version: 3.8.4
Homepage: https://github.com/justinrainbow/json-schema

Package: php-json-schema
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, php5-cgi | php5-cli
Description: PHP implementation of JSON schema
 Validates a php object against a schema. Both the php object and the schema
 are supposed to be a result of a json_decode call. 
 The validation works as defined by the schema proposal in
 http://www.json.com/json-schema-proposal/
